      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer seeking low-cost transportation or a solid project opportunity. It offers strong value for the money, with an honest presentation and the kind of price point that makes it easy to justify. If you need an inexpensive vehicle with potential and room to make it your own, this one deserves a look.",
