      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without all the fuss? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a practical way to get from A to B on a budget. It\u2019s a great fit for someone who wants inexpensive transportation, a backup vehicle, or a project to tinker with. I believe in being straightforward, and this one is priced to make sense for the next owner. If you want a usable car at a wallet-friendly price, come take a look.",
